  <li><img src="http://voog.github.com/wysihtml/img/icn_opera.png" width="24" height="24"> Opera 11+</li>
  <li><strong>Graceful degradation:</strong> Unsupported browsers will get a <i>&amp;lt;textarea&amp;gt;</i></li>
</ul>
